      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is strictly recommended for buyers seeking a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the car suffers from extensive paint peeling, several large dents, and visible rust along the rocker panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
