    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today! Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
