      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a purist's specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit benefits from proactive maintenance, including a documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for the E46 chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing the factory M-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. While the exterior reflects its driver-focused history with minor honest wear, the drivetrain pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline, and the variable M differential lock ensures optimal power delivery out of corners. A superb entry for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
