      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal traction out of apexes. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS hub overhaul. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a factory-spec MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. A true driver\u2019s car, this M3 retains its visceral analog feedback and mechanical integrity.",
